-That's how it should be.

1247
00:45:59,056 --> 00:46:01,191
Hyun-suk who captured
the hearts of New Yorkers.

1248
00:46:02,159 --> 00:46:04,361
-Those look good.
-Choi Hyun-suk.

1249
00:46:04,428 --> 00:46:06,196
