-The patty!

1255
00:46:17,374 --> 00:46:19,443
-It ripped!
-It fell apart!

1256
00:46:19,510 --> 00:46:21,578
-It's smashed.
-It's all broken.

1257
00:46:21,645 --> 00:46:24,581
-It's an emergency!
-It's an emergency!

1258
00:46:24,648 --> 00:46:26,884
