1259
00:46:26,950 --> 00:46:28,619
It's an emergency, Hyun-suk!

1260
00:46:28,685 --> 00:46:30,254
-Let me check it out!
-It's an emergency!

1261
00:46:30,320 --> 00:46:32,790
-It's an emergency, Hyun-suk!
-His patty fell apart!

1262
00:46:33,123 --> 00:46:34,925
