00:48:03,046 --> 00:48:04,414
NICELY SWEET AND SALTY,
PERFECT FOR EVERYONE'S TASTE

1306
00:48:04,481 --> 00:48:06,049
Maple syrup.

1307
00:48:06,116 --> 00:48:07,951
Nobody would hate this.

1308
00:48:08,018 --> 00:48:10,320
That's so good.

1309
00:48:10,387 --> 00:48:11,989
