Refreshingly sour.

1322
00:48:36,280 --> 00:48:38,048
-Yes.
-Perilla leaf.

1323
00:48:38,115 --> 00:48:39,016
Perilla leaf?

1324
00:48:39,082 --> 00:48:40,984
I really love perilla leaves.

1325
00:48:41,051 --> 00:48:44,021
-What? Who?
-Nam-no is using perilla leaves.

1326
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:46,356
-I'm using perilla leaves.
