1336
00:49:10,047 --> 00:49:12,249
ENOKI FRITTER

1337
00:49:13,083 --> 00:49:14,952
DOUBLE-FRIED ENOKI FRITTERS ARE READY!

1338
00:49:17,821 --> 00:49:19,289
This sauce was tangy,

1339
