That's <i>gimbap</i>.

1350
00:49:45,782 --> 00:49:46,616
NOPE!

1351
00:49:46,683 --> 00:49:49,386
Look at him. Look at that face.

1352
00:49:49,453 --> 00:49:50,587
"I'm doing my best."

1353
00:49:50,654 --> 00:49:52,956
It goes in the burger!

1354
00:49:53,023 --> 00:49:55,559
-Wow. That's new.
-He tops the patty with enoki fritters.

1355
00:49:55,625 --> 00:49:58,061
