1370
00:50:28,125 --> 00:50:29,426
-You got this, Nam-no!
-Nine.

1371
00:50:29,493 --> 00:50:31,194
-Eight. Seven.
-Eight. Seven.

1372
00:50:31,261 --> 00:50:33,096
Nam-no finishes too.

1373
00:50:33,163 --> 00:50:35,966
Chef Nam-no, that's a rice ball sandwich.
But you got this!

1374
00:50:36,033 --> 00:50:37,868
Wow. That was amazing.

1375
00:50:37,934 --> 00:50:39,836
That was so amazing.

1376
00:50:39,903 --> 00:50:42,806
That one has a unique shape.

1377
00:50:42,873 --> 00:50:44,775
DID ANYONE ORDER HAMBURGERS?

1378
00:50:44,841 --> 00:50:46,843
That was so amazing.

1379
00:50:46,910 --> 00:50:50,947
And now, both burgers were put together
just for Ye-eun.

1380
00:50:51,014 --> 00:50:52,049
Any thoughts?

1381
00:50:52,115 --> 00:50:54,151
It was so stunning,

1382
00:50:54,217 --> 00:50:55,519
