1383
00:50:55,585 --> 00:50:58,889
-I didn't know it was really 15 minutes.
-We've been doing it for long.

1384
00:50:58,955 --> 00:51:01,058
-This one only took 14 minutes.
-Yes, right?

1385
00:51:01,124 --> 00:51:03,994
First, please try Chef Hyun-suk's burger,

1386
00:51:04,061 --> 00:51:06,797
<i>Five Five Guys.</i>

1387
00:51:06,863 --> 00:51:09,499
NEVER-BEFORE-SEEN ENOKI CHEESEBURGER
WITH SHISHITO PEPPER FRIES

1388
00:51:09,566 --> 00:51:10,500
ARMY BURGER STYLE SAUCE

1389
00:51:11,968 --> 00:51:16,006
A BURGER WITH THE ESSENCE
OF THE 55-YEAR-OLD GUY'S SKILLS

1390
00:51:16,239 --> 00:51:19,810
CHEF CHOI HYUN-SUK'S 55 GUYS

1391
00:51:19,876 --> 00:51:21,111
Do I just dig in?

1392
00:51:21,178 --> 00:51:22,212
Yes, first, eat it as is.

1393
00:51:22,279 --> 00:51:25,015
When you're halfway done,
try the sauce with it.

1394
00:51:25,082 --> 00:51:28,151
-Okay.
-Yes, you hold your burger to eat it.

1395
00:51:28,218 --> 00:51:31,221
-It looks delicious. Thank you.
-The burger enthusiast.

1396
00:51:31,288 --> 00:51:33,390
-The aspiring burger joint owner.
-She eats well.

1397
00:51:34,991 --> 00:51:36,626
-She likes to taste
-That looks good.

1398
00:51:36,693 --> 00:51:39,062
many ingredients in one bite of her food.

1399
00:51:39,129 --> 00:51:40,931
DAZZLING EYES

1400
00:51:40,997 --> 00:51:43,200
Her eyes are dazzling.

1401
00:51:43,266 --> 00:51:44,167
MMM

1402
00:51:44,668 --> 00:51:47,070
She must've had lots of hamburgers.

1403
00:51:47,137 --> 00:51:48,905
But she says nothing. Just a head tilt.

1404
00:51:48,972 --> 00:51:51,975
It's such a wonder that
the mushrooms taste this delicious.

1405
00:51:52,042 --> 00:51:53,310
It looks good.

1406
00:51:53,376 --> 00:51:56,646
I thought the mushroom flavor
would stand out a lot,

1407
00:51:56,713 --> 00:52:00,684
<i>but the balance of the mushroom,</i>
<i>the patty, and the cheese is perfect.</i>

1408
00:52:00,750 --> 00:52:03,186
