1409
00:52:03,253 --> 00:52:05,922
-It's nicely deep-fried.
-I see.

1410
00:52:05,989 --> 00:52:07,057
It's so good.

1411
00:52:07,124 --> 00:52:08,258
-Wow.
-I see.

1412
00:52:08,325 --> 00:52:09,626
It's shockingly delicious.

1413
00:52:10,560 --> 00:52:12,796
He had seasoned the enoki

1414
00:52:12,863 --> 00:52:16,733
