1415
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:19,002
She eats well.

1416
00:52:19,069 --> 00:52:21,071
-The sauce.
-The sauce.

1417
00:52:21,138 --> 00:52:24,541
That's the sauce.
He made it so quickly, yet it was awesome.

1418
00:52:24,608 --> 00:52:26,009
