00:52:27,878 --> 00:52:28,845
ADDED THE SAUCE…

1421
00:52:28,912 --> 00:52:30,280
She tries it with the sauce now.

1422
00:52:31,081 --> 00:52:33,717
DOUBLE THE HAPPINESS

1423
00:52:33,783 --> 00:52:35,185
She looks happy.

