00:52:40,857 --> 00:52:42,025
PERFECT WITH THE SAUCE

1428
00:52:42,092 --> 00:52:43,760
-It's cooked nicely on the inside.
-Yes.

1429
00:52:43,827 --> 00:52:46,496
